[
    {
        "content": "<p>Hello, I am having an issue with an abbreviation not being contracted in the output window. <code>str_substr</code> always remains expanded as in the following example:<br>\n<img alt=\"image.png\" class=\"inline-image\" data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"2088x352\" data-original-src=\"/user_uploads/14278/_5iqs42EBCFkF2myQO4XGHX7/image.png\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/14278/_5iqs42EBCFkF2myQO4XGHX7/image.png/840x560.webp\"></p>\n<p>Even stranger, other abbreviations from the same theory do get contracted. I saw a warning in the thread <a class=\"stream-topic\" data-stream-id=\"238552\" href=\"/#narrow/channel/238552-Beginner-Questions/topic/Not.20to.20expand.20abbreviation.20in.20proof.20state/with/498392229\">#Beginner Questions &gt; Not to expand abbreviation in proof state</a> that locales can keep abbreviations from being folded in, but the abbreviation was not declared in a locale. What do you think could be the problem?</p>",
        "id": 584591645,
        "sender_full_name": "Jibiana Jakpor",
        "timestamp": 1775797690
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><code>n &gt;= 0</code> vs <code>0 &lt;=n</code></p>",
        "id": 584592889,
        "sender_full_name": "Mathias Fleury",
        "timestamp": 1775798820
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>the former is expanded to the latter during parsing</p>",
        "id": 584592919,
        "sender_full_name": "Mathias Fleury",
        "timestamp": 1775798832
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>so your abbreviation needs to be written with <code>0 &lt;= n</code></p>",
        "id": 584592940,
        "sender_full_name": "Mathias Fleury",
        "timestamp": 1775798853
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>(this is an educated guess, because you did not show the abbreviation...)</p>",
        "id": 584593021,
        "sender_full_name": "Mathias Fleury",
        "timestamp": 1775798921
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>That was exactly the issue. This helps me a lot. Thank you so much!</p>",
        "id": 584593566,
        "sender_full_name": "Jibiana Jakpor",
        "timestamp": 1775799348
    },
